doc.title: Dikgokagano tsotlhe
doc.excludeDomains: Tsenya maina a kgolagano ya dikhomphiutha a a tla kgaphelwa thoko Go ka tsenngwa leina la kgolagano ya dikhomphiutha le le lengwe fela ka nako.

example.domain: O ka tsenya leina la kgolagano ya dikhomphiutha, jaaka <khoutu>{{url}}</khoutu>, go kgaphela leina lotlhe la kgolagano ya dikhomphiutha kwa thoko.
example.url: O ka kgaphela dikgokagano tse di rileng kwa thoko ka go tsenya kgokagano, jaaka {{url}}.
example.glob: O ka tsenya paterone ya {{glob}}, jaaka <khoutu>{{tshwano e nnye}}</khoutu>, ya tshwantshanyo e e sa tlhaloganyesegeng.
